{"tid":960569,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《監獄風雲》導演林嶺東驚傳死訊","createTime":"2018-12-29T13:53:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-29T17:57:51.000Z","uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9fca82ceaf942ba72dfef90a11e57212516b96a7","tid":960569,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T13:53:00.000Z","msg":"執導「風雲」三部曲（《龍虎風雲》、《監獄風雲》、《學校風雲》）聞名、現年63歲的林嶺東今午驚傳死訊。警方發言人表示，一名63歲林姓男子在馬鞍山西沙路一單位倒斃，由妻子報案，消息指是導演林嶺東。黑箱車在晚上7時許把遺體送走，其太太和兒子亦目送黑箱車離開，鄰居表示昨日仍跟他打招呼，對此感到十分突然。 <br />\n<br />\n林嶺東擅長拍動作電影，曾以《龍虎風雲》奪得香港電影金像獎最佳導演。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20181229/mobile/bkn-20181229205448359-1229_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20181229%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20181229205448359-1229_00862_001.html&d=GFPEvlzD3uHCEvk4%2BN4tRuargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=24228453\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20181229/mobile/bkn-20181229205448359-1229_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"bdb96bde419ef5a542d3d56315c84d0ebd663a38","tid":960569,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T13:56:48.000Z","msg":"佢老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5703270198c780dce2c46cfa45f275dd0dee7e4b","tid":960569,"uid":39710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T13:56:53.000Z","msg":"2018<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d33244c8105cc31c77cb619327cf427aa86223f","tid":960569,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T13:58:56.000Z","msg":"唔撚係啩，咁樣標尾會"},{"pid":"316172957f95747f61b4f3a0cf4ef5639807fd8f","tid":960569,"uid":218117,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"bdb96bde419ef5a542d3d56315c84d0ebd663a38","tid":960569,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T13:56:48.000Z","msg":"佢老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T13:59:02.000Z","msg":"你噏乜撚呀？"},{"pid":"7805c47ebd80216beddc7bd97e7f1e5b72240f59","tid":960569,"uid":46435,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:34:07.000Z","msg":"R.I.P"},{"pid":"c7a05625ed79312bd60219baca9cd84573d035f7","tid":960569,"uid":42848,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:36:48.000Z","msg":"R.I.P."},{"pid":"d01311c9287f43962ffca34675c47d60565348ee","tid":960569,"uid":41343,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T15:37:15.000Z","msg":"導演林嶺東倒斃家中，藝人張耀揚獲林嶺東力捧，當年的《龍虎風雲》、《監獄風雲》及《學校風雲》令他打響知名度，近年移居澳門的張耀揚收到消息時感到十分愕然，聞訊後即激動爆喊，一度不能開聲！他坦言：「吓！唔係啩？！我希望呢件事唔係真......（對上一次見佢幾時？）兩年前喺杜琪峯飯局......佢一手捧我出嚟，呢樣嘢一世都會記住，我成日想搵機會報答東San（林嶺東暱稱），但未搵到機會。」他表示會冷靜情緒，着記者稍後再致電給他。 <br />\n<br />\n據知，警方接獲林嶺東妻子報案，其妻發現林嶺東倒臥床上，警員到場後，證實林嶺東死亡，初步調查相信事件沒有可疑，林嶺東死因有待驗屍後確定。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20181229/mobile/bkn-20181229220523020-1229_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20181229%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20181229220523020-1229_00862_001.html&d=GFPEvlzD3uHCEvk4%2BN4tRuargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=90e621d3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20181229/mobile/bkn-20181229220523020-1229_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"53f5f35c70a5a8997be5785c0d7c31a44b1a5e2f","tid":960569,"uid":70800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d01311c9287f43962ffca34675c47d60565348ee","tid":960569,"uid":41343,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T15:37:15.000Z","msg":"導演林嶺東倒斃家中，藝人張耀揚獲林嶺東力捧，當年的《龍虎風雲》、《監獄風雲》及《學校風雲》